Diagnosis.
Blue coloured species with elongate, transversal depression running on antero-lateral pronotal area (
Fig. 7A
) and on metasomal tergum I antero-laterally (
Fig. 7A
); posterior propodeal projections markedly diverging (
Fig. 7A
); metascutellar projection narrow and elongate; posterior truncation of apical margin of tergum III narrow, falcate (
Figs 7G, 7H
).
